<h2 class="bold font-l">Zombozo</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Ben must face off against Zombozo, a ghoulish ringmaster clown who steals the energy of others through their laughter. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MonsterClown" class='trope-example-link'>Monster Clown</a></p>
