<h1 id="overlay-title">Zombozo</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Ben must face off against Zombozo, a ghoulish ringmaster clown who steals the energy of others through their laughter.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="ie5g35">
